data.description: Short Sale. ”SHORT SALE.”  Welcome to your charming 2 bed 1 bath home, nestled in a well established neighborhood. This solid block home, has a 2019 roof and a 2016 AC.  One of the highlights of this property is the generously sized fenced in backyard.  The home is minutes away from the Harris Chain-of-Lakes, offering a plethora of water activities right at your fingertips. While the home may need a little cleanup, it presents an exciting opportunity for those looking to add their personal touch and create a space that truly reflects their style and preferences. This property is perfect for first-time homebuyers, a small family, an investor or snow birds.  This home is just an hour's drive from both Orlando and Daytona, minutes from restaurants and shopping and has no HOA!  Schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities that await you in this delightful property.  Buyer is to pay a $5000 buyers premium at closing.
